Post-Match Reflections: Bavuma: 'I'm glad we lost the toss because we were also looking to chase. Things worked out in our favour.'
Cummins: 'Everyone is hurting. We will regroup and try to make amends.'
de Kock: 'It was a great win for the boys. We didn't know how the wicket was going to play and I think we assessed conditions really well.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The pitch was the focus at the toss and Australia decided their bowlers would test it first.
The fielding – and in particular, the catching – was extremely poor and that has to be the first place the Aussies look.
